@flexiarg liberation/noble/right-mindfulness
@title Noble Right Mindfulness: The Mindfulness Faculty Itself
@sigils [👀/天]
@audience practitioners on the path
@tone still
@style liberation-pattern
@path discipline
@tier noble
@references ["liberation/mundane/right-mindfulness (prerequisite)" "liberation/noble/right-effort (effort supports mindfulness)" "liberation/noble/right-concentration (mindfulness enables concentration)"]

! conclusion: Not practicing-mindfulness but the mindfulness faculty operating — "mindfully they give up wrong and take up right" in one intent on the undefiled.

  + context: This operates in one developing the noble path. Mindfulness functions to monitor and guide the giving up of wrong and taking up of right — the awareness that allows course-correction.
    + DISTINGUISHING-FROM-MUNDANE:
      Mundane: "I practice the four foundations" (an I practicing)
      Noble: The mindfulness faculty operating, intent on the undefiled

    + TRANSCENDENT-QUALITY:
      - Not "I am being mindful" but mindfulness happening through one intent on the noble
      - Awareness that neither grasps at clarity nor avoids confusion
      - Monitoring transparent to path-factors
      - The four foundations operating without a meditator

  + IF:
    Even skillful mindfulness involves a meditator — one who takes credit for attention, who is proud of presence. Mindfulness can become another identity-project.

  + HOWEVER:
    Awareness continues — the question is whether it flows from identification or from the path functioning.

    + THE-RUNNING-CIRCLE:
      Right mindfulness is one of the three that run and circle around all the other factors: "Right view, right effort, and right mindfulness" — the mindful giving up of wrong and taking up of right.

    + WORN-AWAY:
      "For one of right mindfulness, wrong mindfulness is worn away. And the many bad, unskillful qualities that arise because of wrong mindfulness are worn away."

  + THEN:
    Noble right mindfulness is the awareness faculty operating in context of the path — "mindfully they give up wrong and take up right" — but the 'they' is transparent. Awareness arising as expression of path, not as personal accomplishment.

  + BECAUSE:
    Right mindfulness runs and circles around all the other factors — it is what allows each factor to be practiced with clarity rather than blindly. Noble right mindfulness is this monitoring awareness functioning without a monitor separate from the awareness.
